12
00:01:18,928 --> 00:01:20,663
Woo Joo.

13
00:01:21,697 --> 00:01:24,242
Adorable.

14
00:01:24,242 --> 00:01:25,743
Oh, you brought your car?

15
00:01:25,743 --> 00:01:27,461
Yeah.

16
