Finding a spot was rough,

17
00:01:43,344 --> 00:01:44,887
plus the roads were packed,

18
00:01:44,887 --> 00:01:46,741
so I kept worrying I'd be late.

19
00:02:00,528 --> 00:02:03,614
We will now begin

20
00:02:03,614 --> 00:02:04,949
the Saetbyeol Daycare

21
00:02:04,949 --> 00:02:06,784
Little Stars Recital.

22
00:02:06,784 --> 00:02:08,853
What is it?

23
00:02:08,853 --> 00:02:10,371
It's nothing.

24
00:02:10,371 --> 00:02:12,456
When's Woo Joo's turn again?

25
00:02:13,499 --> 00:02:16,301
He's in the second act.

26
00:02:17,837 --> 00:02:18,988
